      "content_blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "2026-05-27"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "What's New"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "OpenAPI V2.0 Public Cloud Edition Released"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "items": [
            "Building on the capabilities opened in V1.0, this version adds query interfaces for various business modules, covering organizations and projects, member permissions, live stream forwarding and sharing, flight tasks and records, map annotations, and more — further meeting the integration needs of third-party platforms for information queries.",
            "This version also optimizes the API system by separating the public cloud and private cloud API documentation, making API categorization clearer for developers to quickly understand and integrate, and allowing OpenAPI to enter a more agile iteration cadence."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Live Share 2.0 Supports Sharing Multiple Devices at Once"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "items": [
            "Live sharing has been fully upgraded to support adding multiple device live streams to a single share link."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "FlightHub 2 Copilot Now Supports DJI Dock 2"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "items": [
            "FlightHub 2 Copilot, the intelligent drone control assistant, now supports DJI Dock 2."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Feature Optimization"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Automated Workflow Adds Trigger Configuration and Notification Module"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "items": [
            "Automated workflow now supports trigger and notification configuration, allowing more flexible workflow triggering and outbound notifications of workflow status."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "More Updates"
        },
        {
          "type": "list",
          "items": [
            "The FlightHub project page menu can now be expanded to display menu names.",
            "Notifications such as virtual cockpit AI alerts and automated assignment workflows now support sound alerts."
          ]
        }
      ],
